{"tid":356123,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"諗起當年有個靚女同我考中文 oral","createTime":"2017-08-11T20:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T05:12:27.000Z","uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc72d78cc16aef2a6acc69354f5e1fabe11ee093","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:31:41.000Z","msg":"個時一 grp 5條友，法國個靚女講野好有 sense。係拔苗助長條題目拎咗周杰倫做例子<br />\n<br />\n之後有條死肥仔打斷我發言，然後一輪嘴咁講咩德智體群育<br />\n<br />\n之後考完佢同我講：啱啱條友打斷你講野一定 lv 1<br />\n<br />\n最後唔知點解，拎lv 1個人係我，但係個靚女個臉孔就令我念念不忘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3673adf3e166435e068abb5d3cecbd0705b6fab","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:36:14.000Z","msg":"個女仔有幾分似龔嘉欣，如果當時有問佢拎 contact ，而唔係將自己 contact 比咗派問卷個姐姐，我同佢今日又會發展成點？<br />\n<br />\n記得走個時我同佢並肩咁落樓梯，每一級我心入面都暗暗咁倒數<br />\n<br />\n可惜我連佢叫咩名都唔知，到走嘅時候望住龔嘉欣嘅背影漸漸消失"},{"pid":"372c57962d5a8105c2379bc7cb1ff93bf884c1d9","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:40:46.000Z","msg":"之後考中文閱讀之前又咁啱見到個女仔，佢自己一個係欄邊拎住丫丫 lam 嘅筆記睇，並未察覺我已走近佢身邊<br />\n<br />\n最後開考前佢終於望過黎，只係 say 咗個。 Hi ，然後入去考<br />\n<br />\n考完之後我再冇見過咁似龔嘉欣嘅女仔，唔知你依家過成點，不過你靚得黎又帶幾分文學氣息，又有幾分仙氣"},{"pid":"ce340adc6c16bf2a8f8164dd5d8fac3feef786b7","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:43:51.000Z","msg":"人生有好多見得一兩次，甚至緣慳一面嘅人，特別係一個似龔嘉欣嘅女仔"},{"pid":"1f355c3eed6a8dd358ed35d8cbbc8fa779a03c5b","tid":356123,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dee6c17334f5ef1fd8b4b1cf5df6d3f877fd74","tid":356123,"uid":65656,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:45:33.000Z","msg":"訓啦"},{"pid":"3829562958ab55101a43cfa3c62995dbf89af33c","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:51:42.000Z","msg":"到考完中文後，一直好期望可以見返你，一次都已經足夠，但係考完英文 oral 後都見唔到你<br />\n<br />\n如果可以見多你幾次，我可能已經忘記咗你，又可能同你做咗個朋友。但係正正因為冇可能見到，我先一直記住<br />\n<br />\n之後我習慣每隔幾個月都搵龔嘉欣嘅相睇下，會唔會有你幾分嘅影子係入面，好可惜，見唔到。<br />\n<br />\n你比我印象最深刻嘅，就係似龔嘉欣。"},{"pid":"b28cf6e42868695bef5e941d22a3bb194a135cf5","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪個女仔？如果係就唔好同我講，我想一直沉溺係回憶中"},{"pid":"b3c92bfa066f64adfe2dc6cd3d39b7f51a883329","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T20:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓啦</blockquote><br />\n早抖"},{"pid":"99efabd4b0f12e24de95d2d56673efd2c9e9e0ac","tid":356123,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f848adfa5cbd41198471d443d5e97a4c05d533","tid":356123,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8011269e80e6491cc7e3871db9930d16dd1d1514","tid":356123,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff858eec87a8217be2fa8f79d2e7b709d89be4ac","tid":356123,"uid":55256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之後考中文閱讀之前又咁啱見到個女仔，佢自己一個係欄邊拎住丫丫 lam 嘅筆記睇，並未察覺我已走近佢身邊<br />\n<br />\n最後開考前佢終於望過黎，只係 say 咗個。 Hi ，然後入去考<br />\n<br />\n考完之後我再冇見過咁似龔嘉欣嘅女仔，唔知你依家過成點，不過你靚得黎又帶幾分文學氣息，又有幾分仙氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早知你行過黎啦屌，唔撚想理你呀<br />\n幾撚辛苦呀，份notes我睇完好撚耐啦，但我都要扮睇緊就係唔想你行埋離<br />\n開考逼住要轉身咪同你say聲hi囉屌<br />\n<br />\n為左避你我特登提早交卷呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"52ed9d314c8792e3fefda530883cfaf65d3bf05c","tid":356123,"uid":68916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:32:31.000Z","msg":"靚女似一個樣衰既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8882ab2d878817a521060fb8b5080fbe81a764a5","tid":356123,"uid":31787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"Ff怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7138d85e732f8c2681de6730400b15cfdf5be382","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之後考中文閱讀之前又咁啱見到個女仔，佢自己一個係欄邊拎住丫丫 lam 嘅筆記睇，並未察覺我已走近佢身邊<br />\n<br />\n最後開考前佢終於望過黎，只係 say 咗個。 Hi ，然後入去考<br />\n<br />\n考完之後我再冇見過咁似龔嘉欣嘅女仔，唔知你依家過成點，不過你靚得黎又帶幾分文學氣息，又有幾分仙氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早知你行過黎啦屌，唔撚想理你呀<br />\n幾撚辛苦呀，份notes我睇完好撚耐啦，但我都要扮睇緊就係唔想你行埋離<br />\n開考逼住要轉身咪同你say聲hi囉屌<br />\n<br />\n為左避你我特登提早交卷呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係咁"},{"pid":"0138e0ebd8810e01e28dfbac9916a98b1a8832e7","tid":356123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夜晚訓唔著 9up ，小馬有冇一啲見過一面嘅人但係仲記得佢嘅存在？"},{"pid":"c4bea6e54378500b5ee6d36fd170b933381152f8","tid":356123,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e0007d0303f9e54cff9d772836e8268d7c7347","tid":356123,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:04:49.000Z","msg":"覺得可惜就想像下如果佢係肥婆你仲會唔會咁念念不忘<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2